items.name: BanG Dream! Girls Band Party! (style, 30+ characters)
items.description:
A LoRA (Hadamard Product) based on 2396 Girls Band Party cards, recognizing 34 characters to varying degrees.

A multi-character experiment that turned out better than expected on the first try. Capable of generating multiple subjects, although the consistency still isn't quite there. Decent at hair but often messes up eye colors with multiple subjects.

Usage

This Hadamard Product LoRA requires installing an extra extension to be used in the Web UI.

When prompting for multiple characters, it's recommended to use the following format:

MainChar/OtherChar1/OtherChar2, other tags ...

Training info

Dataset:

  • 2396 Cards collected from Bandori Party

Tags generated with SmilingWolf/wd-v1-4-convnextv2-tagger-v2 with a threshold of 0.35. No balancing and tag cleaning.

The data source also provides info about which other characters are also present in the card art ("cameos"). However, this info is not precise enough, as cards often have two images featuring different characters. Generated tags were used to determine if the cameo characters' names should be included in the caption.

The caption template is MainChar/OtherChar1/OtherChar2..., other tags shuffled. Although slashes were used as the character separator, using commas instead doesn't seem to noticeably degrade performance.

Trained for 40 epochs but it is not clear if that many were required. The 10-epoch checkpoint is already usable. All checkpoints can be found on the hf repo.

Training cost: ~13 T4 hours

items.name: Delicate Armor-精致铠甲
items.description:
给你的模型添加不可思议的细节！

使用了最新的LyCORIS模型，提供超乎想象的细节感。记得看大图感受细节。也欢迎查看我的其他lora模型：ttplanet Creator Profile | Civitai

注意事项，由于webui没有内置LyCORIS使用前一定要记得安装插件,

最新的lora block weight或者additional networks插件有bug，会造成prompt中的lora提示词失效，请谨慎安装！

the most updated lora block weight or additional networks plugin are with bugs, it will make the lora command in prompt inactive, please wait I delete this line to update, otherwise you can't use Lycoris!

https://github.com/KohakuBlueleaf/a1111-sd-webui-locon

然后使用传统的方式调用lora, 比如： <lora:delicate_armor_V2:0.6>

那么接下来让我们开始吧：

  • 由于我完全分开了所有装备，大家可以自由穿搭。常见的词如下：盔甲 armor,全身盔甲 full armor, 腿甲 cuisses，护肩 shoulder armor, 头盔 helmet, 腰带 belt, 护手 glove或者hand guard, 靴子 boots, 兜帽 hood, 法师帽 wizard hat, 法师服 wizard robe, 当然也不仅限于这些，所有的穿搭的物品都会自动被加上细节。以上装备也能给修饰词，进行调整变形，具体根据你的底模决定。

  • 请在开头放上delicate\(armor\)触发模型，由于是LyCORIS模型，需要安装我提示的插件后，使用<lora:模型名字:权重>进行触发，千万不要忘记，插件勾选的方式目前不支持。

接下来我就把创造的空间留给大家了，我的参考图仅仅只是参考，并没有测试各种动作，controlnet的影响，但是这是我经过很多版测试带给你们的版本，在自由度上还是很不错的。

模型可以匹配基本所有SD 1.5的底模，并带来各种意想不到的效果，希望大家多尝试。

Add incredible details to your model!

Introducing the latest LyCORIS model, offering an unimaginable level of detail.

Please note, the webui does not have LyCORIS built-in, so remember to install the plugin before using it:

https://github.com/KohakuBlueleaf/a1111-sd-webui-locon

Then, use the traditional method to invoke Lora, like this: lora:delicate_armor_V2:0.6

Let's get started:

Since I've separated all the equipment, you can mix and match freely. Common terms include: armor, full armor, cuisses, shoulder armor, helmet, belt, glove or hand guard, boots, hood, wizard hat, wizard robe, and more. Any items you wear will automatically have details added. You can also modify the above equipment with adjectives to adjust and transform them, depending on your base model.

Please start with delicate\(armor\) to trigger the model. Since it's a LyCORIS model, after installing the plugin I mentioned, use <lora:model_name:weight> to trigger it. Don't forget, the current plugin selection method is not supported.

Now, I'll leave the creative space to you. My reference images are just for reference and have not been tested for various actions or the impact of controlnet. However, this version has gone through many tests and offers great freedom in terms of customization.

The model can match almost all SD 1.5 base models and bring unexpected effects. I hope you'll give it a try.

items.name: IZ*ONE_Yabuki Nako
items.description:
Introduction: Yabuki Nako is an active member of the Japanese girl group HKT48 Team H under EMI Records and a former member of the South Korean-Japanese girl group IZ*ONE under Off The Record Entertainment. source

Fourth LoRA with controlled amount of datasets, probably my best work so far, at the moment, this is what I used:

Model: ChilloutMix_NiPrunedFp32Fix (works best to handle the hairs)/ Basil_mix_fixed (works pretty good as well)
Sampling: DPM++ SDE Karras
Sampling: 20 to 30
Hires steps: 20
Size: 512x768
CFG Scale: 4 (recommended), but still getting good result with 7
LoRA strength: 0.8(best result), 0.9-1 (good result, but will have some noise with the hairs)
Face restoration: GFPGAN 0.5

CLIP skip: 2
Use the usual VAE

Upscaler: Nearest , upscale by x2
Denoising: 0.49

Hires fix is optional

Highly encouraged to use CLIP skip 2

It's not perfect, but I hope this LoRA is worth your time and the time I spent making this.

If you feel like supporting, do leave a tip at my kofi page


It took a lot of hours of hard work and dedication, so any kinds of support is very much appreciated :) :)

Thank you so much!!

items.name: Tutu/Ballet outfit - LoHa
items.description:
Please check out my Ko-Fi page if you are interested in supporting me.

LoRA commissions open! -> Fiverr

This is a LoHa LoRA! You need the extension! Why? They do a lot better with multi-concepts.

This is retrained from thesauceer dataset, just a version of his Tutu LoRA, please check out his original work! He was kind enough to share his dataset.

Trigger words for V3.20:

positive: <lora:Tutuv320:0.5>(tutu)

You can also try WITH VERSION V2.20: "ribbon-trimmed skirt", "layered skirt" and "miniskirt".
If failing to make full shirt, try adding either "leotard" or "tank top" or "covered navel" to prompt.

Keep in mind you might have to adjust LoRA and/or tag weight for it to appear, defaults to "ribbon-trimmed skirt" most of the time! Dataset wasn't an exactly split between the different concepts.

Follow the steps in the Model Version notes to reproduce my images.

Sample images generated with Hassaku.

All negative embeds should be easy to find. and Prompts should be included in the sample images! Click the little icon in the bottom right to see it.

It was trained on 45 512x512 images provided by thesauceer, 20 epochs using Animefull-final-pruned for the Training Model.

Danbooru tags generated by Waifu Diffusion 1.4 Tagger.

modelVersions.name: v3.20
modelVersions.description:
Generate using a weight of 0.3-1.0 like this: <lora:Tutuv220:1>.

Trimmed and improved dataset and new training settings on an attempt to improve consistency and quality of ribbon skirts.

How I archived my generations:

  1. txt2img: DPM++ SDE Karras with 20 steps, 512x512(can go up to 768 for wide or tall), Restore faces on (using CodeFormer weight 1.0 in Settings), Hires-fix on, to 1024x1024 (double original size) with your preferred upscaler and Denoise 0.4, CFG 7. Then send to img2img!

  2. img2img: DPM++ SED Karras with 20 steps, Restore faces on (CodeFormer weight 1), rescale to 1536x1536, CFG 7, Denoise between 0.3-0.7 (based on how much you want to improve the image), SAME PROMPT! Send to extras when happy with img2img/inpaint results.

  3. extras: Scale to x3 (final will be 4608x4608, I suggest going lower, I did x3 just for the samples here) Upscaler 1 - FatalAnime 4x, Upscaler 2 - SwinIR 4x with 0.10 visibility, GFPGAN 0.10 visibility, CodeFormer 0.10 visibility.

If anyone is curious about my version names: v{version}.{trainingEpochs}

items.name: 【Costume】Erotic Jiangshi (China Zombie) Costume 涩情僵尸装
items.description:
V3:

There is more trigger words now for flexibility (you can tweak the clothes to make certain parts of the body exposed more easily )and more stable outputs.

现在有更多的触发词，提升了灵活性（你可以通过调整衣服让身体的某一部分更轻松地暴露出来），并有更稳定的结果。

When using V2 you might find ofudas got lost (especially on certain photorealistic models) or brought large areolaes, now that is solved.

用V2时你可能会发现胸前的符咒丢了（特别是用在某些真人模型上时）或是让乳晕变得很大，现在这个问题解决了。

Multires noise enabled.

金字塔噪声也开了。

And after lots of experiment it seem that "jiangshi" might bring a weird hand gesture, is that caused by NAI's clip or something?

经过大量测试，似乎"jiangshi"会带来一种奇怪的手势，这会跟NAI的clip或是别的什么有关吗？

Well, "jiangshi" actually is not necessary but will make qing_guanmao more stable. If you do not want to input "jiangshi", you can try "qing_guanmao, hat"

"jiangshi"实际上不是必须的但是会让清官帽更稳定，或者如果你不想写"jiangshi"，你可以试试"qing_guanmao,hat"。

"China dress" might cover the breasts with some models, so you can also try "pelvic curtain" instead of that.

"china dress" 在一些模型上可能会把胸口遮了，所以你也可以试试用"pelvic curtain"替换之。

=================

Anime lora trained on NAI.

I really like the concept of ero jiangshi (just like Jwah Jah).

As for this lora, it is the combination of Qing_guanmao, ofuda_on_nipples, detached_sleeves and cheongsam. Well, maybe it is a Hwah Jah cosplay lora.

When you input tag "qing_guanmao" without loras like this, it is very easy to get a hat similar to Hu Tao (Genshin Impact)'s hat, but of course that is not the true qing_guanmao on a classic jiangshi's head.

基于NAI训练的二次元lora。

我真挺喜欢涩情僵尸的概念（类似华甲）。

至于这个lora，它是“清官帽”，“符咒遮奇酷比”，“分离式袖子”和“旗袍”的结合。额，或许确实像是个华甲Cos lora。

当你在没有类似这样的lora的情况下输入“qing_guanmao”时，很容易得到一款类似胡桃的帽子，但显然那不是经典的僵尸头上的清官帽。

In February of 1934, the German Heereswaffenamt (Army Weapons Agency) ordered the creation and adoption of a new military rifle. Mauser derived the Karabiner 98k from a number of its earlier rifle designs, namely the Mauser Standardmodell of 1924 and the Karabiner 98b, which in turn had both been developed from the Gewehr 98. The Kar98k would be one of the final evolutions of the prolific Mauser series of bolt-action rifles.

Like other German Mauser rifles, the Kar98k quickly earned a reputation for being reliable and accurate. Although supplemented by semi- and fully automatic firearms during World War II, the Kar98K remained the primary German infantry rifle until the end of the war in 1945. Following World War II, massive numbers of Kar98k rifles were captured and distributed by both the Soviet Union and Western forces to allied states across the globe. One of the most notable (and ironic) users of the Kar98k after World War II was the newly-founded state of Israel, which received a large amount of Kar98ks and converted them to 7.62×51mm NATO. The Kar98k, along with its wartime contemporaries the Lee-Enfield and Mosin Nagant, still sees much use on the battlefields of today.

items.name: Z_phyr Portraits (2.1 768)
items.description:
Warning: includes both safe content and unsafe content.

This model was trained by me with Dreambooth on 1456 pictures and then merged with 10 other photorealistic models.

Works best on realistic portraits. Trained on close-up, head, shoulder and chest portraits of people of different races, sex and age, with different lighting conditions, with different facial expressions and body gestures.

All examples are generated without face restoration and hires fix and they don't seem to be necessary, but you can use them when things get really bad.

Contains a noise offset.

Contains booru tags.

警告：包括安全内容和不安全内容。

这个模型是我用 Dreambooth 对 1456 张图片进行训练，然后与其他 10 个逼真的模型合并。

在写实的人像上效果最好。接受过不同种族、性别和年龄的人的特写、头部、肩部和胸部肖像的训练，在不同的灯光条件下，有不同的面部表情和身体姿态。

所有的例子都是在没有 face restoration 和 hires fix 的情况下生成的，它们似乎没有必要，但当事情变得非常糟糕时，你可以使用它们。

包含一个 noise offset。

包含 booru 标签。

Предупреждение: включает как безопасное, так и небезопасное содержимое.

Эта модель была обучена мной в Dreambooth на 1456 фотографиях и затем объединена с 10 другими фотореалистичными моделями.

Лучше всего работает на реалистичных портретах. Обучался на близких, головных, плечевых и грудных портретах людей разных рас, пола и возраста, с разными условиями освещения, с разной мимикой лица и жестами тела.

Все примеры сгенерированы без face restoration и hires fix, и они не кажутся необходимыми, но вы можете использовать их, если дела совсем плохи.

Содержит noise offset.

Содержит теги booru.

items.name: ShinYunBok
items.description:
Shin Yun-bok, better known by his pen name Hyewon (1758–1813), was a Korean painter of the Joseon Dynasty. Like his contemporaries Danwon and Geungjae, he is known for his realistic depictions of daily life in his time.

Suggested prompt: "best quality, shinyunbok painting, <your prompt>"
Suggested negative prompt: "worst quality, low quality"
You can adjust the strength, like (shinyunbok painting:0.7) to weaken the style.

v1.0, v2.0 - Train Base model : https://huggingface.co/runwayml/stable-diffusion-v1-5
v2.0 Animation - Train Base model : SilvermoonMix Base v1.2
v2.0 Animation SD2.1 - Train Base model : Replicant-V3.0
SDXL - Train Base model : https://huggingface.co/stabilityai/stable-diffusion-xl-base-1.0

========================================================================

For v2.1 specific - Train Base model : Waifu Diffusion - Beta 03

Suggested prompts: "shinyunbok anime, (exceptional, best aesthetic, new, newest, best quality, masterpiece, extremely detailed, waifu:1.2), <your prompt>"
Suggested negative prompt: "((photo, realistic)), lowres, ((bad anatomy)), ((bad hands)), missing finger, extra digits, fewer digits, blurry, ((mutated hands and fingers)), (poorly drawn face), ((mutation)), ((deformed face)), (ugly), ((bad proportions)), ((extra limbs)), extra face, (double head), (extra head), ((extra feet)), monster, logo, cropped, worst quality, jpeg, humpbacked, long body, long neck, ((jpeg artifacts)), deleted, old, oldest, ((censored)), ((bad aesthetic)), (mosaic censoring, bar censor, blur censor)"

v2.1 mercury SD2.1 - strong Shin Yun-bok style
v2.1 venus SD2.1 - slightly weak Shin Yun-bok style and leaning on Japanese anime style

========================================================================

All trained images are from https://gongu.copyright.or.kr/
Training Datasets : https://huggingface.co/datasets?search=bebechien

items.name: VAZ 2108/2109/21099
items.description:
ВАЗ-2108 «Спутник» (простореч. названия «восьмёрка» или «зубило»[2]) — советский и российский переднеприводной автомобиль II группы малого класса с кузовом типа хэтчбек. Разработан и серийно выпускался на Волжском автомобильном заводе в 1984—2004 годах[3]. Представлял собой базовую модель в семействе моделей Лада «Спутник». C 2004 года на конвейере автомобиль был заменён рестайлинговой моделью ВАЗ-2113.

ВАЗ-2109 «Спутник» (простореч. название «девятка»[1]) — советский и российский переднеприводной автомобиль II группы малого класса с кузовом типа хэтчбек. Разработан и серийно выпускался на Волжском автомобильном заводе в 1987—2004 годах. С 2004 до конца 2011 года вариант ВАЗ-21093 собирался из машинокомплектов на Украине на заводе «ЗАЗ». Представляет собой пятидверную модификацию ВАЗ-2108 в семействе моделей Лада «Спутник».

ВАЗ-21099 «Спутник» (простореч. название «девяносто девятая»[1][2][3]) — советский и российский легковой автомобиль II группы малого класса, первый переднеприводной седан Волжского автомобильного завода. Представляет собой наиболее полноразмерную модель в семействе «Лада Спутник».

Машина была подготовлена к конвейерному выпуску в марте 1990 года, но начало производства было отложено в связи с задержкой в поставках комплектующих от предприятий-смежников[4]. Серийно выпускался на заводе АвтоВАЗ с 22 декабря 1990 года по 30 июня 2004 года. До конца 2011 года собирался на Украине на заводе «ЗАЗ» из российских машинокомплектов с элементами салона от ВАЗ-2115. На экспорт ВАЗ-21099 шёл под названиями Lada Forma, Lada Sagona, Lada Diva, Lada Sable,

modelVersions.name: v1.20
modelVersions.description:
Generate using a weight of 0.5-1.0 like this: <lora:ButterflyWingsV120:0.75>.


How I archived my generations:

  1. txt2img: DPM++ SDE Karras with 20 steps, 512x512(can go up to 768 for wide or tall), Restore faces on (using CodeFormer weight 1.0 in Settings), Hires-fix on, to 1024x1024 (double original size) with your preferred upscaler and Denoise 0.4, CFG 7. Then send to img2img!

  2. img2img: DPM++ SED Karras with 20 steps, Restore faces on (CodeFormer weight 1), rescale to 1536x1536, CFG 7, Denoise between 0.3-0.7 (based on how much you want to improve the image), SAME PROMPT! Send to extras when happy with img2img/inpaint results.

  3. extras: Scale to x3 (final will be 4608x4608, I suggest going lower, I did x3 just for the samples here) Upscaler 1 - FatalAnime 4x, Upscaler 2 - SwinIR 4x with 0.10 visibility, GFPGAN 0.10 visibility, CodeFormer 0.10 visibility.

If anyone is curious about my version names: v{version}.{trainingEpochs}
